free_txt: Corrected by SD and VV: Corrections in all
thin AE layers followed by four thick E-layers.
Associated particles were detected in TOF, an array
of plastic scintillator time-of-flight detectors of
dimensions 200 x 50 x 3000 mm long mounted vertically
Statistical errors. Systematic errors are the
polarized photons. The photon energy resolution was
~ 2 MeV and the total photon flux, over the 114 to
792 MeV tagged photon energy range was ~ 5 x 10**8/s.M
Data from Figs. 2 - 11 were compiled at the
Russia MSU SINP CDFE by V.Varlamov.
Effect of uncertainty in TOF thresholds.
